You're thinking of the Zoo Hypothesis! It proposes that advanced alien civilizations are deliberately avoiding contact with humanity to allow us to evolve without interference, like wildlife in a sanctuary 
Beyond "Fermi's Paradox" VIII: What is the Zoo Hypothesis? - Universe Today
.

But your story takes it way darker - and this is brilliant educational material:

Current Reality: Humanity is currently Type 0.72 on the Kardashev Scale, expected to reach only Type 0.74 by 2060 
IFLScience
Nature
. We can't even harness all of Earth's energy yet.

The Kardashev Scale Basics:

Type I: harness all planetary energy
Type II: harness entire star's energy (Dyson Sphere)
Type III: harness entire galaxy's energy
Type IV: manipulate cosmic structures 
Kardashev scale - Wikipedia
Your Story's Twist: The Conclave isn't waiting for humanity to be ready - they're actively preventing advancement through the infiltration network. This solves a real scientific mystery: why humanity's violent impulses and weapons of mass destruction might destroy us before we reach higher types 
Kardashev scale - Wikipedia
.

Educational Integration Through Ahdia:

Her Processing: "Wait, so we're not even a Type 1? We're like... a .7? That's like getting a D-minus on your cosmic report card. And these Type IV beings are what, PhDs in reality manipulation? Great. My mom's one of them and she still uses shame tactics. Advanced technology, bronze-age parenting."

The Infiltration Reveal: When the team discovers 40% of leadership are interdimensional beings, it answers real questions about why humanity can't unite to solve global problems. Not just human greed - actual non-humans keeping us divided to prevent Type 1 advancement.

The Stakes: Type 1 civilizations can control weather, volcanoes, deflect asteroids, and master space travel 
Type 1 | Kardashev Scale Wiki | Fandom
. The Conclave fears a unified humanity achieving this.

This makes complex astrophysics personally relevant - readers learn why we're stuck at 0.72 through a story about systematic oppression!

